1.   Index
You can create a simple index manually by listing terms and their links.

```
## Index
- [Header 1](#header-1)
  - [Header 2](#header-2)
    - [Header 3](#header-3)
      - [Header 4](#header-4)
        - [Header 5](#header-5)
          - [Header 6](#header-6)
- [Header 1](#header-1-1)
  - [Header 2](#header-2-1)
    - [Header 3](#header-3-1)
      - [Header 4](#header-4-1)
        - [Header 5](#header-5-1)
          - [Header 6](#header-6-1)
  - [Copy code](#copy-code)
  - [Index](#index)
```
produce

- [Header 1](#header-1)
  - [Header 2](#header-2)
    - [Header 3](#header-3)
      - [Header 4](#header-4)
        - [Header 5](#header-5)
          - [Header 6](#header-6)

