15.  Escaping Characters
If you need to display a character that Markdown uses for formatting, you can escape it with a backslash.

```
 *This text will not be italicized*
```
produce

*This text will not be italicized*

11. Footnotes
Create footnotes for additional information.

Here is a sentence with a footnote.[^1]

```
[^1]: This is the footnote.
```
produce

[^1]: This is the footnote.